research_municipality_step.notes: Fate, Texas operates under a Council-Manager form of government, which is a variation of the mayor-council system. The City Council consists of a Mayor and six Council members, all elected at-large. There is a recall petition against Councilwoman Codi Chinn that was filed on January 5, 2026. Elections for Council Member Places 2 and 3 are scheduled for May 2, 2026.
